OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1781387266
OL,3,C'Brexit has cost the company #1
OL,4,Cmillion'
OL,6,FA leading manufacturer has told UTV
OL,7,Fthat a decade of Brexit has cost the
OL,8,Fcompany #1 million.
OL,10,FIt's 10 years since the United Kingdom
OL,11,F(UK) voted to leave the European Union
OL,12,F(EU).
OL,14,FBrexit changed everything as much of
OL,15,Fwhat came after was unknown at the
OL,16,Ftime.
OL,18,FThere were high stakes negotiations
OL,19,Fbetween governments as well as
OL,20,Fpolitical turmoil.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
