FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1781387266
OL,3,C'Brexit has cost the company #1
OL,4,Cmillion'
OL,6,FPolitical arguments for and against
OL,7,FBrexit continue to rumble on but
OL,8,Feconomically, companies are still on a
OL,9,Fjourney as they deal with the
OL,10,Fcomplexities which have emerged.
OL,12,FWhile the politicians were responsible
OL,13,Ffor the negotiations, it was the
OL,14,Fbusinesses on the ground who had to
OL,15,Fmake it all work.
OL,17,FIn Bangor, more than four million
OL,18,Fhairbrushes are manufactured each year.
OL,20,FDenroy has invested in production
OL,21,Ffacilities and skilled staff.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1781387266
OL,3,C'Brexit has cost the company #1
OL,4,Cmillion'
OL,6,FUTV spoke to the company multiple
OL,7,Ftimes during the Brexit negotiations
OL,8,Fabout their fears and concerns.
OL,10,FAs part of UTV's current affairs
OL,11,Fprogramme Up Close, we spoke to the
OL,12,FCEO.
OL,14,FKevin McNamee said "I told you ten
OL,15,Fyears ago that Brexit wasn't going to
OL,16,Fbe a good idea.
OL,18,F"It was going to add bureaucracy, it
OL,19,Fwas going to cost every business right
OL,20,Facross the UK.
OL,26,@vD@TOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1781387266
OL,3,C'Brexit has cost the company #1
OL,4,Cmillion'
OL,6,F"Guess what? That's a fact," he added.
OL,8,F"We've had a significant increase in
OL,9,Fthe whole bureaucracy around import
OL,10,Fand export of goods.
OL,12,F"That has required us to employ
OL,13,Fadditional people, to put processes in
OL,14,Fplace.
OL,16,F"We're getting hit with tariffs, that
OL,17,Fweren't in place beforehand.
OL,19,F"So was it a good idea? No, it wasn't
OL,20,Fa good idea."
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@AOUtD@AOUxD@AOU{D@AOU|D@MO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1781387266
OL,3,C'Brexit has cost the company #1
OL,4,Cmillion'
OL,6,FThere have been many calculations
OL,7,Fabout the cost of Brexit.
OL,9,FDenroy has been able to calculate a
OL,10,Fdirect impact on its business.
OL,12,FKevin McNamee told Up Close "it's
OL,13,Fprobably in the region of over #100k a
OL,14,Fyear".
OL,16,F"We're ten years in. So that's #1
OL,17,Fmillion. We could have done other
OL,18,Fthings with that million quid.
OL,26,@xD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1781387266
OL,3,C'Brexit has cost the company #1
OL,4,Cmillion'
OL,6,F"We could have invested in more
OL,7,Fequipment, we could have paid
OL,8,Fadditional salaries, we could have
OL,9,Femployed additional people," he added.
OL,11,F"It's lost money, a million pounds
OL,12,Fgone."
OL,14,FThere were fears about a hard border
OL,15,Fon the island of Ireland for many
OL,16,Fyears.
OL,18,FHowever, after deliberations and
OL,19,Fcampaigns, the border has landed in
OL,20,Fthe Irish Sea.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUtD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
