FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1781387266
OL,3,C'Brexit has cost the company #1
OL,4,Cmillion'
OL,6,FIt is a situation which is both
OL,7,Fpolitically and economically
OL,8,Fdifficult, resulting inchecks on goods
OL,9,Fcoming from Great Britain (GB) to
OL,10,FNorthern Ireland (NI).
OL,12,FThe government has implemented the
OL,13,FWindsor Framework, which has resulted
OL,14,Fin green and red lanes to reduce
OL,15,Fchecks.
OL,17,FIf that was a perfect solution why is
OL,18,Fthe government pursing an agri-food
OL,19,Fdeal with the EU?
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1781387266
OL,3,C'Brexit has cost the company #1
OL,4,Cmillion'
OL,6,FThe reality is that difficulties still
OL,7,Fexist.
OL,9,FLynas Foods is a company which is
OL,10,Fhaving to navigate the complexity.
OL,12,FManaging Director Andrew Lynas said
OL,13,F"The Brexit journey has felt like a
OL,14,Flong journey where every stage, you get
OL,16,Fdifferent information.
OL,18,F"Its been deeply frustrating
OL,19,Fespecially in the food business."
OL,26,@uD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1781387266
OL,3,C'Brexit has cost the company #1
OL,4,Cmillion'
OL,6,FOn the current arrangements, he said
OL,7,F"I'm an all Ireland business, and so
OL,8,Fif I'm going to sell any of my
OL,9,Fproducts into the Republic of Ireland,
OL,10,Fthey all go through the red line.
OL,12,F"We haven't seen a huge benefit.
OL,14,F"I think it's helped retailers, but I
OL,15,Fheard lots of stories about the wins
OL,16,Fthat Brexit could be right across what
OL,17,FI'll call 'Northern Ireland PLC'.
OL,19,F"Unfortunately, we haven't seen it,"
OL,20,Fhe added.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUvD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1781387266
OL,3,C'Brexit has cost the company #1
OL,4,Cmillion'
OL,6,F"I can send my goods to Scotland every
OL,7,Fnight but I can't bring certain goods
OL,8,Fback without masses of paperwork.
OL,10,F"I'm a logical person. That just
OL,11,Fdoesn't make sense to me. Cheese I
OL,12,Fcould have ordered today in Wales
OL,13,Fcould have been here tomorrow.
OL,15,F"It's now a seven to 14 day lead time
OL,16,Fand we need five to seven bits of
OL,17,Fpaperwork."
OL,19,FOverall, NI is in a unique position
OL,20,Fcompared to the rest of the UK.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUwD@AOUyD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
