FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1781387266
OL,3,C'Brexit has cost the company #1
OL,4,Cmillion'
OL,6,FThe area can sell unrestricted into
OL,7,FGreat Britain and into the EU - dual
OL,8,Fmarket access is the official term.
OL,10,FAnecdotally people describe it as one
OL,11,Ffoot in the EU and one foot out, or
OL,12,Fthe best of both worlds.
OL,14,FPolitically for some that is difficult
OL,15,Fas it means NI remains subjected to EU
OL,16,Frules, but economically it has a
OL,17,Fbenefit to some businesses.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1781387266
OL,3,C'Brexit has cost the company #1
OL,4,Cmillion'
OL,6,FLinwoods Health Foods in Armagh sells
OL,7,Facross the UK but a large portion of
OL,8,Ftheir business is with countries like
OL,9,FSpain.
OL,11,FManaging Director Patrick Woods said
OL,12,F"30% of our sales go into the EU."
OL,14,F"Being able to export freely into GB
OL,15,Fand into Europe is a huge benefit to
OL,16,Fus.
OL,18,F"We in NI have essentially the best of
OL,19,Fboth worlds. We can export freely to
OL,20,Freach markets."
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@bO]vD@AOUzD@AOU|D@OO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44513
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1781387266
OL,3,C'Brexit has cost the company #1
OL,4,Cmillion'
OL,6,F"As an organic business, we see it
OL,7,Fwith potentially our competitors in
OL,8,Fthe UK who are exporting into Europe,
OL,9,Fhave a lot higher barrier and a lot
OL,10,Fmore difficulty to access the European
OL,11,Fmarkets."
OL,13,F"We are in a better position than they
OL,14,Fare and the dual market access has
OL,15,Fbeen key to that."
OL,17,F"Without that, we would have been
OL,18,Fsignificantly hampered."
OL,20,FCatch up with Up Close: A Decade of
OL,21,FBrexit.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@IO]uD@AOUwD@RO]yD@AOUzD@XO]
